Raspberry Pi library for GPIO, 1-Wire, System Time Counter (STC) access. As an
example of usage there has been provided API for handling various popular sensors
like Dallas DS family of temperature sensors, HC-SR04 distance sensor, PISO shift
register.

Expect more detailed documentation and sensors support in the future. For now
look for examples in /examples directory.

